data.description: BUILDER'S SPECIAL! You will love this brand-new home in a quiet neighborhood. Close to all the Branson activities, including all the lakes, but a little out of the tourist crowd. Very well done home from head to toe, offering three bedrooms with two bathrooms and a spacious living, dining, and kitchen area, giving you over 1,300 sqft. You will appreciate all the high-end finishes and materials, like the excellent textured paint on the walls, the white subway tile in the kitchen, a custom-built pantry and walk-in closet with a farm door, an oversize insulated one-car garage, LED lights, and pre-wired for CAT-5 ethernet throughout. AS A BONUS, NO RESTRICTIONS ON NIGHTLY RENTAL,  so this is your chance to own your vacation home in the woods and OFFSET your expenses when you are not using it. One-year Builder's warranty included. DON'T MISS THIS ONE! 2023-02-15
